Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美利坚歌颂你时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会否知晓  你的辉煌经历
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会否知晓  你将历史改写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界从此不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船已驶入港口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能否看到他
