Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人玷污他的名声  美利坚遗忘他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与他同抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为他牺牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱戴他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是傻瓜  射杀了他
