Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1776年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问您是亚隆·伯尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看是谁在问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  我是亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为您效劳  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我在普林斯顿就久仰大名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽快完成学业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我跟您的校友商量这件事时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能打了他  记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他负责财务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打了财务长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我想步您的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年毕业  加入革命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的眼神说我在犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么能提前毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我父母的遗愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是孤儿  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿有一场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们能证明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的价值高于他人期望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着聊天  我给你个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别向他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表露你的喜恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口无遮拦的傻瓜下场凄凉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演时间  表演时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是约翰·劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了两扎啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力提升酒量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些英国兵与我不和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不争得独立誓不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  亲爱的  我是拉法耶特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命骑士来也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远道而来说"晚安"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向国王说"放马过来"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁最强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是赫拉克勒斯·穆里根  有种就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到你母亲喊着"再来一次"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管好你们的女儿和马匹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身穿四套束腰  很难宽衣解带欢爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说放荡话  再来一杯酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再举杯敬革命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是普林斯顿的奇才吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚隆·伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱一首  说一段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝好运  你表态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上场  我欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看谁笑到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔  革命即将到来  你还犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从不表态  伯尔  你究竟相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子是谁  他要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正如我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻  好斗  迫切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拿到国王学院的奖学金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}哥伦比亚大学的前身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多半不该吹嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真该死  我这么出色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题在于我脑筋灵光却不懂逢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得呐喊才有人肯听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的每句话都充满智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是未经雕琢的璞玉  闪闪发光的煤炭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想方设法  实现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演说才能  无懈可击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年方十九  思想成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约街道  愈发寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩担重任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥补缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身无武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍饥挨饿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我计划让这星星之火燎原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真该死  天要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我说出我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是  亚  历  山  大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们  一  见  如  故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本该自治的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却被英国肆意欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键他们收税无情无义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转身就被乔治国王挥霍无理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他绝不会解放他的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本世纪内定有革命掀起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该我登场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他请出自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你在历史课上学到我  不必讶异
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿献出生命换取自由权利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终你们会见证我出人头地
