Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.02,0:26:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.10,0:26:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.17,0:26:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寡不敌众  部署落后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.76,0:26:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.46,0:26:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一位左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.75,0:26:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.25,0:26:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排炮阵地被轰击  清点损失伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.30,0:26:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要阻止他们  灭灭他们的风头
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.34,0:26:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝赐我们毅力  我们要坚定立场
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.94,0:26:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿绝不弃船而逃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.29,0:26:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去偷敌人的火炮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.63,0:26:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮声隆隆  血肉横飞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.68,0:26:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮声隆隆  我们弃守基普斯湾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.23,0:26:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一艘船被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.13,0:26:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼哈顿岛南端失守
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.69,0:26:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得迅速撤到哈莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.68,0:26:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再败一场我们都遭不住
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.51,0:26:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,备好武器鞍马  我决定分散兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.98,0:26:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英军攻城略地  我军人心惶惶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.49,0:26:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就要放弃  千夫所指
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.28,0:26:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对叛变的众人  我高喊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.07,0:26:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我要跟这群人保卫美利坚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.55,0:27:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们夜奔行军  远远望着曼哈顿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.23,0:27:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分身乏术  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.14,0:27:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我急需辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.81,0:27:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-尊敬的长官  -你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚隆·伯尔  长官  可以说说我的想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你请便
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.85,0:27:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  我曾是蒙哥马利将军麾下的上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.22,0:27:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他在魁北克颈部中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.84,0:27:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  我觉得自己能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.48,0:27:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敬佩您一直从远处向英军开火
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.30,0:27:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有几个问题  想提几个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.86,0:27:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要抗击  而不是西逃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.02,0:27:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请讲  -那么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.89,0:27:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  您要见我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.24,0:27:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  进来  你认识伯尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.11,0:27:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-认识  长官  我们总碰到  -我们总碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.76,0:27:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才说  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.04,0:27:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待您的战略发挥成效
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.58,0:27:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-伯尔  -长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去后把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做错什么了吗  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你过来是因为我们的胜算太渺茫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.87,0:27:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大名如雷贯耳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.68,0:27:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我忍不住发笑  -长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.97,0:27:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  怎么就没人把你招致麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.66,0:27:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.94,0:28:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会我  你是个有名望的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.96,0:28:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在市区战斗时你偷了英军的火炮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.90,0:28:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳瑟内尔·格林和亨利·诺克斯都想将你收入靡下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做他们的秘书  我才不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.75,0:28:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你有何不满  -我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.74,0:28:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  你想战斗  你迫切立功
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.70,0:28:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我年轻时跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满心都是作为烈士赴死的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.49,0:28:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.93,0:28:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去反而轻松  年轻人  活着才更艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.02,0:28:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-为什么要跟我说这些  -我说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.60,0:28:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手上的资源只有国会许诺的三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.02,0:28:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是个快要爆炸的火药桶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.23,0:28:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你这样的人帮我减轻负担
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.71,0:28:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.70,0:28:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.61,0:28:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我正如我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.22,0:28:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}年轻  好斗  迫切
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.86,0:28:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子  我们武器不够  兵力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.20,0:28:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您需要所有的帮助  我有些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.56,0:28:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳伦斯  马利根  拉法耶特侯爵  还缺什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.44,0:28:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}寡不敌众  部署落后
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要敌人内部的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.72,0:29:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找些敷衍了事的英王手下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给国会写信申请物资
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.91,0:29:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您召集人马  出其不意攻其不备
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄不问出处  我来整合情报
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.17,0:29:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我们建立新的国家  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.20,0:29:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}将军驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.71,0:29:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.79,0:29:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}将军驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.71,0:29:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.81,0:29:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.25,0:29:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}将军驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.71,0:29:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起义
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.71,0:29:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}将军驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.20,0:29:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.72,0:29:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.12,0:29:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私生之子  孤苦之人  荡妇之子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.96,0:29:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能风生水起  成为现象级人物
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.13,0:29:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睁睁看着这个讨人厌的傲慢大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.51,0:29:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当上国父的得力助手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.52,0:29:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华盛顿当场任用汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.15,0:29:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但汉密尔顿依然想上战场  不想做文职
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.70,0:30:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿的笔杆子本事确实出色
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.36,0:30:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说我们都有什么共同点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.38,0:30:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是姑娘们的好伴侣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.08,0:30:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}姑娘们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.33,0:30:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娇嫩欲滴任人采撷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.84,0:30:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}姑娘们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.98,0:30:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  变凤凰的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.53,0:30:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}姑娘们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.63,0:30:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们让他欣喜  也迷了他的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.87,0:30:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莎·华盛顿给捡回的公猫取了他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.58,0:30:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确有其事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.00,0:30:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1780年  冬日舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.04,0:30:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人艳羡斯凯勒三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.72,0:30:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能娶到其中一位  你就发了  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.19,0:30:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是能不能娶到  还是娶哪一位  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.09,0:30:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意  我愿意  我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.78,0:30:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望着你的双眼  深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.45,0:31:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.80,0:31:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.85,0:31:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来不是爱抢风头的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.91,0:31:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个热情的夜晚  我们跟叛军一同狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.91,0:31:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑话我姐姐  因为她让全场意乱情迷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.79,0:31:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你走进来  我的心突然狂跳
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.97,0:31:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想从舞厅的一侧吸引你的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.02,0:31:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在跳舞  乐队放开音量演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.11,0:31:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏着节奏  我们享受美酒佳肴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.74,0:31:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抓住我姐姐悄声道  "这人我要了"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.14,0:31:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐姐穿过舞厅走向你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.21,0:31:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好紧张  想着"她要干什么"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.14,0:31:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她抓住你的胳膊  我想"我完蛋了"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.27,0:31:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看向我  我突然情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.18,0:31:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你动人的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.32,0:31:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}望着你的双眼  深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.90,0:31:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我情难自禁  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.44,0:31:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.55,0:31:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.16,0:32:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.52,0:32:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}望着你的双眼  深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.87,0:32:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.25,0:32:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.44,0:32:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.98,0:32:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要带我去哪里  -我要改变你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.05,0:32:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.71,0:32:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白·斯凯勒  幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.27,0:32:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯凯勒  -我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.20,0:32:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你浴血奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.00,0:32:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若我们相识的代价就是开战
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.59,0:32:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这仗打得也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.11,0:32:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.89,0:32:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周后  我每晚挑灯写信
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.91,0:32:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每收到你的一封信  我都觉得生活更加美好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.99,0:32:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑话我姐姐  因为她想做你的女眷
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.96,0:32:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说说而已  你真爱我的话  就跟我分享他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.13,0:32:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两周后  在客厅里我焦虑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.08,0:32:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我父亲寻求祝福  但他板着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.11,0:32:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们吃吃喝喝  我急得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.90,0:32:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强忍泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.39,0:32:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只要你想  无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.31,0:32:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲穿过房间来到你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.32,0:32:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间我慌了神  想着"我们完蛋了"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.35,0:33:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他握了握你的手  说"要忠贞不渝"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.43,0:33:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你转身笑着望向我  而我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.66,0:33:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.52,0:33:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}望着你的双眼  深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.30,0:33:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.59,0:33:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.65,0:33:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.57,0:33:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.52,0:33:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的意中人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.61,0:33:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}望着你的双眼  深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.56,0:33:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.21,0:33:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.71,0:33:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.76,0:33:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莱莎  我身无一文
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.49,0:33:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名下无地  麾下无兵  默默无闻
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.82,0:33:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有道义气节  百折不挠
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成绩优异  聪明绝顶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.83,0:33:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来疯狂  你们一家唤醒我的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.80,0:33:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩吉向我吐露真言  安洁莉卡想占有我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.80,0:33:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心  我对你的爱毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.49,0:33:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以去哈莱姆定居  开启新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.50,0:33:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自小孤苦伶仃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.53,0:33:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲离家  母亲离世
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.31,0:33:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是个野孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.63,0:34:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我永远都无法忘却我母亲的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.67,0:34:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我还活着  伊莱莎  我对天发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.03,0:34:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝不会受那些苦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.23,0:34:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.53,0:34:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意  我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.82,0:34:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莱莎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.14,0:34:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.60,0:34:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}我愿意  我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.85,0:34:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我从未如此
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.17,0:34:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.35,0:34:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}我已为你沉沦  我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.85,0:34:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我的人生将一片光明  因为有了伊莱莎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.55,0:34:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.30,0:34:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.56,0:34:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.30,0:34:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望着你的双眼  深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.51,0:34:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}为你沉沦  淹没在脉脉眼波中
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.67,0:34:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人到纽约  改头换面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.27,0:34:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.87,0:35:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.50,0:35:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  有请伴娘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安洁莉卡·斯凯勒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.49,0:35:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举杯敬新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.98,0:35:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}敬新郎  敬新郎  敬新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.84,0:35:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.81,0:35:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}敬新娘  敬新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.45,0:35:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.91,0:35:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.75,0:35:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直陪伴在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.37,0:35:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.19,0:35:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬你们喜结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.95,0:35:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}敬美利坚  敬革命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.31,0:35:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你们自强不息
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.15,0:35:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}自强不息  自强不息
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.82,0:35:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你们永远
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.25,0:35:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}永远
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.88,0:35:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.18,0:35:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}时光倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.59,0:35:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.21,0:35:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}深邃无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.22,0:35:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}淹没
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.69,0:35:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}时光倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.91,0:36:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}回忆起那晚  我可能
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.53,0:36:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}时光倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.81,0:36:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}回忆起那晚  回忆起...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.68,0:36:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆起那晚
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能会为此后悔一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.58,0:36:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那群年轻气盛的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.88,0:36:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急不可耐地想要讨我们欢心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.43,0:36:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那如梦似幻的烛光
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.23,0:36:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此虚无缥缈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远忘不了与你初见的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就此不同
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那睿智的双眼  精瘦的体格
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.42,0:36:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我问声好  我便忘却自己姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑拨起我心中的火焰  燃遍全身
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.97,0:36:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来  你好像从未满足过
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.57,0:36:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么  你逾越了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.34,0:36:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样  我就从不满足
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.57,0:36:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未满足
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.85,0:36:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安洁莉卡·斯凯勒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.06,0:37:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.44,0:37:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家世如何
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.55,0:37:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不重要  志向千千万  我才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你等着瞧  你等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.11,0:37:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是斗智斗勇
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.72,0:37:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋逢对手的感觉  这里头肯定有诈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.46,0:37:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉如同重见光明
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.32,0:37:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同富兰克林风筝迎闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.01,0:37:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三两分钟的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.84,0:37:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们便情投意合
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.54,0:37:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是一场梦  一支舞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.31,0:37:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故作姿态  摆明立场
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽风流  但我也愿意给个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.17,0:37:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,询问起家况  他竟那样答复
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.20,0:37:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他局促不安  眼神躲闪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.08,0:37:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身无分文  摸爬滚打
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.17,0:37:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那样一表人才
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零星的胡须  稚气仍未脱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.24,0:37:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带他远远逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.74,0:37:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但转身看见我的妹妹  她已经
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.00,0:37:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道她已经
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.81,0:37:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.93,0:37:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的眼神已经
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.09,0:37:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时我意识到三大基本真理
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.69,0:37:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要带我去哪里  -我要改变你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.75,0:38:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.38,0:38:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.88,0:38:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只用嫁给一个富人家
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}事实上她父亲有数个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是家父不曾育有儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.64,0:38:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得靠我来攀附权贵
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.04,0:38:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是最聪明的长女
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.55,0:38:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而纽约城满是流言蜚语
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.32,0:38:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然亚历山大身无分文
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.93,0:38:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱意也丝毫不会减
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白·斯凯勒  幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.97,0:38:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯凯勒  -我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.02,0:38:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.53,0:38:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他追求我  只因我是斯凯勒家千金
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.58,0:38:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能提升他的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.16,0:38:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛开这点也太天真  正是因此
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.19,0:38:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才给他介绍伊莱莎  如今已是他的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好  安洁莉卡  他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不会满足
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.30,0:38:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你浴血奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.69,0:38:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若我们相识的代价就是开战
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.18,0:38:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这仗打得也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.72,0:38:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.20,0:38:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对我妹妹了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.41,0:38:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不会有人像她那般纯真善良
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.52,0:38:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我对她诉衷肠  她会默默成全
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.16,0:39:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将属于我  而她会故作轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.99,0:39:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那都是假装
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.78,0:39:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个夜晚  我都会想起亚历山大的双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.11,0:39:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会幻想  若我没有断然评判他
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.48,0:39:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.21,0:39:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少亲爱的伊莱莎是他的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.46,0:39:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我还能见到他那双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.20,0:39:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.12,0:39:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}敬新郎  敬新郎  敬新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.05,0:39:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.17,0:39:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}敬新娘  敬新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.58,0:39:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.08,0:39:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}安洁莉卡  安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.91,0:39:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直伴你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.42,0:39:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}伴你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.37,0:39:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬你们喜结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.26,0:39:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}敬美利坚  敬革命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.50,0:39:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你们自强不息
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.39,0:39:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}自强不息  自强不息
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.17,0:39:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你们永远
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.35,0:39:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}永远
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.05,0:40:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.93,0:40:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.68,0:40:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.46,0:40:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会是幸福的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.60,0:40:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.55,0:40:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他永远都不会满足
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.76,0:40:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远也不会满足
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.92,0:40:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有生之年  我见不到辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.07,0:40:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有生之年  我见不到辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.10,0:40:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我至少见过大小奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.54,0:40:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我至少见过大小奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若野猫都能成婚
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.73,0:40:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大都能成婚
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.72,0:41:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明我们都有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.57,0:41:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举杯敬自由
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.72,0:41:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后可不再是自由身
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.76,0:41:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管她如何交代你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.42,0:41:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举杯敬我们四人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.19,0:41:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬刚刚脱贫的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.52,0:41:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会讲述今夜的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.09,0:41:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.54,0:41:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这不是亚隆·伯尔吗  -先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.95,0:41:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没想到你真的会来  -肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.55,0:41:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-伯尔  -我是来道喜的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.60,0:41:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来一段  伯尔  -大家伙儿都在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.30,0:41:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最差劲了  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.65,0:41:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别理他们  祝贺你  陆军中校
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.90,0:41:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望和你一样领军
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.27,0:41:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是保管乔治的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.89,0:41:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你才不想  -我真想
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.31,0:41:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放明智一点
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.65,0:41:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你成了不可或缺的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.91,0:41:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是听说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.17,0:41:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你金屋藏娇  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.92,0:41:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.95,0:41:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在隐瞒什么  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.83,0:41:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我该走了  -不  该走的是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.37,0:41:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别来烦我们  -别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.16,0:42:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.81,0:42:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚把那姑娘带来多好  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.51,0:42:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说真好  但恐怕我做的是不法勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.39,0:42:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么意思  -她结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.14,0:42:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-懂了  -她嫁给了一位英国军官
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.64,0:42:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.81,0:42:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次恭喜你  亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.60,0:42:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.06,0:42:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们战场上见
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.40,0:42:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远理解不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.36,0:42:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你爱这个女人  就去追求她
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.11,0:42:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.74,0:42:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们战场上见
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.75,0:42:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们战场上见
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}西奥多西娅与第一任丈夫育有三女两子\N在他因伤去世后嫁给伯尔  育有一女
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西奥多西娅每天给我写信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.89,0:42:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当她丈夫不在时  我替她暖床
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.81,0:42:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在乔治亚替英国而战
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.02,0:43:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想让殖民地井井有条
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.98,0:43:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可以留着整个乔治亚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.78,0:43:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但西奥多西娅  她是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.61,0:43:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情不分罪人圣徒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.03,0:43:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不断索取  我们仍付出真心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.62,0:43:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们哭笑  我们粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.41,0:43:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.75,0:43:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多男人屡试未果
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.39,0:43:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假若她有青睐我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.21,0:43:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我愿意等待
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.88,0:43:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意等待
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.47,0:43:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}乔纳森·爱德华是大觉醒运动的领袖\N被视为美国基督精神之父\N他的布道《落在愤怒之神手中的罪人》享有盛誉\N曾任普林斯顿校长
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.47,0:43:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我外公是个作风严厉的牧师
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.64,0:43:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有布道和赞美诗传授不了的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.98,0:43:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母亲是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.44,0:43:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天才
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.85,0:43:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲备受尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.78,0:43:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.77,0:43:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们去世时未留下只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.32,0:43:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有需保护的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.57,0:43:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡不分罪人圣徒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.82,0:43:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不断索取  我们仍努力拼搏
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.49,0:43:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们起落  我们粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.36,0:43:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.62,0:44:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有爱过我的人逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.25,0:44:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假若我有活着的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.25,0:44:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.54,0:44:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.80,0:44:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.34,0:44:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.88,0:44:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.97,0:44:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能掌握自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.51,0:44:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待  等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.10,0:44:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法效仿  独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.64,0:44:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待  等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.23,0:44:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不落后  也不迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.69,0:44:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待  等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.23,0:44:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不坐以待毙  而是伏击等待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.45,0:44:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿前方漫漫长路
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.49,0:44:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要证明自我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.75,0:44:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他失无可失
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.75,0:44:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿步履不停
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.42,0:44:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不虚度光阴
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.75,0:44:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是何种感受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.22,0:44:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿从不犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.89,0:44:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他无拘无束
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.93,0:45:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不断索取
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.48,0:45:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一直取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.40,0:45:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.86,0:45:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加大赌注
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.73,0:45:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存的人寥寥无几
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.40,0:45:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假若他有所向睥睨的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.61,0:45:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我愿意等待
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.86,0:45:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.99,0:45:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意等待
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.08,0:45:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活不分罪人圣徒
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.33,0:45:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不断索取
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.46,0:45:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我们仍努力拼搏
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.21,0:45:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们起
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.25,0:45:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我们起落  我们粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.00,0:45:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我们犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.04,0:45:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们落
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.71,0:45:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数不清的人逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.80,0:45:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假若我有活着的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.67,0:45:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.26,0:45:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.93,0:45:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.37,0:46:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.21,0:46:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.43,0:46:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过将军如此沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.39,0:46:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接手掌管他的所有通信
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.35,0:46:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会来信  "乔治  向英军进攻"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.27,0:46:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回复  "我们已开始杀马果腹"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.65,0:46:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本地商户拒绝为我们提供装备和协助
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.90,0:46:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只收英国货币
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.19,0:46:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱一首六便士之歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.11,0:46:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-救兵不来了  -但长官
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.99,0:46:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历克斯  我们想赢只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.78,0:46:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激起民愤
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.29,0:46:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.37,0:46:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开火  夜里突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.62,0:46:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚守阵地  直到对方撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.54,0:46:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让英军无法辩解战争的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.84,0:46:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跑得快  -跑得快
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.26,0:46:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抗得久  -抗得久
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.30,0:46:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进攻  速撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.68,0:47:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持活到这场恐怖秀结束
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.80,0:47:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将要祭奠许多同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.27,0:47:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举杯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.23,0:47:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回到纽约  继续做学徒
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.94,0:47:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请求法国援助  希望法国能派船只
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.02,0:47:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我继续跟着汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.59,0:47:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撰写反奴隶制的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.32,0:47:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都是对我们友情和勇气的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.99,0:47:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我们切断补给线
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.49,0:47:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷窃走私货
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.28,0:47:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择各自的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.62,0:47:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.28,0:47:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天  "长官  请允许我领军"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.20,0:47:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-而每一天  -不行
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.58,0:47:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都立刻否决我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.58,0:47:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.71,0:47:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取而代之他却提拔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.25,0:47:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯·李
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.09,0:47:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他成为副指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.67,0:47:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.92,0:47:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我不会选择他
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孟莫斯之役他落荒而逃
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.84,0:47:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-各位  进攻  -撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.85,0:47:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-进攻  -撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.56,0:47:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  李  赶紧好好指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.27,0:47:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对方人数众多  -不好意思  这不合你心意
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.56,0:47:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汉密尔顿  -准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.69,0:47:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让拉法耶特指挥  -遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.82,0:47:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千名士兵死于38度高温
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.44,0:47:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们勉强打成平手  逃过一败
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.57,0:48:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯·李成了弃子  身败名裂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.66,0:48:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要人愿听  他便开口讲
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.83,0:48:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放任华盛顿一意孤行
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.21,0:48:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优柔寡断  危机不断
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.04,0:48:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对革命最大的贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.29,0:48:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是回弗农山种烟草
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.59,0:48:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也别做
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.63,0:48:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史会证明他是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.51,0:48:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但长官  -我们还有仗要打
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.43,0:48:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.76,0:48:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李出言挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.91,0:48:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须向他挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.60,0:48:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能违抗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.14,0:48:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.23,0:48:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大  你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.77,0:48:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳伦斯  不要放过良机射偏
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.32,0:48:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七  八  九
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.49,0:48:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是决斗十诫
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.49,0:48:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是决斗十诫
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.29,0:48:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.38,0:48:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战目的在于满意
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.88,0:48:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对方道歉  则无需决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.55,0:48:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.30,0:49:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若不道歉  找个朋友做你的副手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.80,0:49:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的副官
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.68,0:49:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替你做最后的清算
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.72,0:49:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.39,0:49:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方的副手面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.02,0:49:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行和平谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.22,0:49:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或定下时间和地点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.52,0:49:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常见的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.60,0:49:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其在新兵之间
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.98,0:49:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数纷争  不战而消
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.94,0:49:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.90,0:49:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法达成一致
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.31,0:49:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.32,0:49:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿把手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.53,0:49:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让医生待命
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.24,0:49:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提前付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.68,0:49:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼貌待人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.45,0:49:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他转身
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.53,0:49:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便事后推诿
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.50,0:49:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.37,0:49:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对决要在太阳升起前
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.75,0:49:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找个困兽之地赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.42,0:49:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.17,0:49:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给至亲留张字条
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.23,0:49:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们你去哪拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.96,0:49:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷天堂或地狱对你敞开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.84,0:49:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.51,0:49:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忏悔罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.38,0:49:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你见到对手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好肾上腺素飙升
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.85,0:49:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.64,0:49:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的协商机会
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.02,0:49:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派出副手  看是否能澄清误会
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.73,0:49:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亚历山大  -亚隆·伯尔  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.77,0:49:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能否同意对决即愚蠢又幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.36,0:50:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  但你的人要为言行付出代价  伯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.20,0:50:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用他的生命吗  我们都明白这太荒唐  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.95,0:50:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  有多少人的死
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.62,0:50:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为李缺乏经验  行事鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.16,0:50:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  看来非决斗不可
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.37,0:50:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第九
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.58,0:50:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着对方的眼睛  别瞄高了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.83,0:50:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起全部勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.21,0:50:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后数数
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.09,0:50:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七  八  九
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.63,0:50:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-几步  -十步
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.01,0:50:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.01,0:50:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李  你投降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.30,0:50:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你击中他的侧身  他投降
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.64,0:50:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我满意了  -我们得清理现场
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.98,0:50:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.10,0:50:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.52,0:50:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有好戏看了  -这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.15,0:50:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔先生  给将军叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.44,0:50:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.07,0:50:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李  你我永远看不对眼
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.03,0:50:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.86,0:50:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些年轻人无法代表我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.99,0:50:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-您辛苦了  -我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.12,0:50:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汉密尔顿  -长官
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.45,0:50:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.08,0:50:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你谈谈  跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.12,0:50:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你谈谈  跟你谈谈  跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.92,0:50:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-孩子  -别叫我孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.25,0:51:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便没有内讧这仗已很难打
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.29,0:51:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李向你挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.34,0:51:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们就向他挑战  -你这样解决不了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.01,0:51:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你激怒了我们南方的盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.88,0:51:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.97,0:51:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰就该一枪打烂他的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.47,0:51:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他彻底闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.51,0:51:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-孩子  -我不是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.60,0:51:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.35,0:51:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是需要人保护的弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.35,0:51:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我能处理好  -查尔斯·李  托马斯·康威
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.93,0:51:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人四处败坏你的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.31,0:51:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经历过许多非议  我能承受
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.48,0:51:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没有你的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.52,0:51:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你的头衔  没有你的领地
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.69,0:51:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但如果你...  -不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.73,0:51:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你给我一个营  让我带领这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.99,0:51:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能战后一举成名
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.36,0:51:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可能丧命  你必须活着
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.82,0:51:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.12,0:51:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妻子需要你活着  孩子  我需要你活着
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.75,0:51:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再叫我一次孩子试试
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.96,0:51:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧  亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.55,0:51:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是司令下达的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.01,0:51:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.38,0:51:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.23,0:52:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看如今世事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.65,0:52:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻我们活着是多么幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.19,0:52:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看看  仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.28,0:52:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.95,0:52:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-大概一个月  -伊莱莎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.87,0:52:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早该告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.45,0:52:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个月前写信给将军
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.92,0:52:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -我求他准你解甲归田
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.50,0:52:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早该告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.00,0:52:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.55,0:52:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我知道你会战斗至最终胜利  -战争还未结束
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.18,0:52:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你应该有机会见见自己的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.81,0:52:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这世事  看这世事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.22,0:52:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻我们活着是多么幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.44,0:52:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甘愿做穷人的妻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.31,0:52:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他无法为你带来富足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.15,0:52:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甘愿做你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.91,0:52:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这世事  看这世事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.58,0:52:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你如今的成就
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.00,0:53:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想你曾一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.83,0:53:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着就是个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.25,0:53:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活着便已足够
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.88,0:53:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.01,0:53:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一分你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.60,0:53:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一分你的抱负
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.60,0:53:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这世界来说
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.98,0:53:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便已足够
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.02,0:53:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会假装理解
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.44,0:53:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所面对的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.95,0:53:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在头脑中反复
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.62,0:53:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推翻重建的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.58,0:53:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.25,0:53:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.08,0:53:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你最终能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.30,0:53:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便已足够
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.88,0:53:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不需要万世流芳
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.30,0:53:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不需要家财万贯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.64,0:54:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我能为你带来安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.06,0:54:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你能对我敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.44,0:54:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我成为这故事的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.15,0:54:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未来人们会写下的史书中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.40,0:54:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让此刻成为第一个篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.49,0:54:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿意留下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.04,0:54:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便心满意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.59,0:54:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说就已足够
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.51,0:54:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便已足够
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.94,0:54:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣衫褴褛  自发组织  乌合之众
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.91,0:54:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟想打败一位世界霸主
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.70,0:55:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们如何从进退两难转败为胜
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.29,0:55:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让贝特西·罗斯的星条旗高高飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.29,0:55:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}被美国公众广泛认作国旗的首位制作者
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.25,0:55:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们有个秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.92,0:55:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位你们熟知且喜爱的移民  他不惧挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.63,0:55:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不断地把大不列颠的走狗耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.38,0:55:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家欢迎美利坚最喜爱的法国战士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.26,0:55:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}拉法耶特
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.06,0:55:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手执缰绳策马飞奔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.18,0:55:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这些英国兵血溅三尺
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.77,0:55:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}拉法耶特
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.56,0:55:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会停止  将他们打败  将他们毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.27,0:55:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将他们挫骨扬灰  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.35,0:55:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}拉法耶特
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.15,0:55:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打得他们屁滚尿流落荒而逃怒火中烧  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.73,0:55:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}拉法耶特
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.32,0:55:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去法国筹钱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.48,0:55:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}拉法耶特
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.19,0:55:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回来更多的武器和船只
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.74,0:55:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让战局扭转
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.49,0:55:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跟罗尚博会师  联合我们的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.99,0:55:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能在约克镇结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.08,0:55:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们败于海上
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.29,0:55:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要想成功我们仍需另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.71,0:55:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.23,0:55:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.92,0:55:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  他熟悉战壕作战
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.25,0:55:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机敏过人且法语流利
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.79,0:55:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.42,0:55:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总归要用到他的才智
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.96,0:55:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他场外观战有何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.30,0:55:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.92,0:55:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人比得上他的应变能力
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.26,0:55:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没人能媲美我的天才战术
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.76,0:56:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.39,0:56:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想夺回自己的土地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.60,0:56:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.22,0:56:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要找回我的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.60,0:56:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.26,0:56:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找回你的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.43,0:56:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.56,0:56:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白需要找回你的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.27,0:56:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.52,0:56:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得给他写封信  越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.00,0:56:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.35,0:56:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找回你的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.48,0:56:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.07,0:56:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队正在战场上等你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.61,0:56:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你此刻加入
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.70,0:56:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以携手扭转战局
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.12,0:56:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.58,0:56:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵们都在等你号令
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.38,0:56:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们打好这场战役
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.80,0:56:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们将在破晓时投降
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.26,0:56:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界从此不同
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.97,0:56:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.41,0:57:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次领军杀敌时
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.91,0:57:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你现在还要年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.79,0:57:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我领手下冲进一场屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.13,0:57:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼目睹他们的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.92,0:57:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾犯下无数过错
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.09,0:57:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中愧疚与日俱增
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.05,0:57:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至今日我深夜难眠
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.56,0:57:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深知我所做的一切  自有历史评判
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.86,0:57:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的一切  自有历史评判
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.79,0:58:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻时的我梦想荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.88,0:58:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多希望那时我就懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.16,0:58:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法左右
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.89,0:58:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁生  谁死  谁讲述你的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.97,0:58:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们能获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.98,0:58:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你怀有远大抱负
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.31,0:58:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你记住  从此刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.61,0:58:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的一切  自有历史评判
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.00,0:58:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的一切  自有历史评判
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.80,0:58:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约克镇战役
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.56,0:58:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1781年
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.94,0:58:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汉密尔顿先生  -拉法耶特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.23,0:59:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-终于来到战场  你的归属  -完全没在怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.90,0:59:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于来到战场  这一路可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.53,0:59:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是移民
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.44,0:59:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成事还得靠我们
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.95,0:59:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-要是战胜你有什么打算  -我要回法国
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.32,0:59:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有机会  我要解放我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.74,0:59:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我们将全力支持
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.16,0:59:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  带领你的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.25,0:59:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-江湖再见  -后会有期  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.79,0:59:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.25,0:59:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.46,0:59:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正如我的国家  年轻  好斗  迫切
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.01,0:59:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.55,0:59:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.93,0:59:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.44,0:59:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.10,0:59:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时常想象死亡  熟悉得如同回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.48,0:59:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的死期  站着等敌人袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.44,0:59:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若人生终于此处  至少有朋友知己
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.94,0:59:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手握武器  带领士兵  并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.57,0:59:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我想起伊莱莎在家等我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.99,0:59:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此  伊莱莎即将临盆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.45,0:59:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须战斗  我们必须胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.41,0:59:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立新的国家  迎接我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.83,0:59:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把子弹从枪中卸掉  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.30,0:59:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-子弹卸掉  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.46,0:59:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗中前行
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.54,1:00:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们整齐划一
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.83,1:00:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着夜色偷袭  成败在此一举
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.21,1:00:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让走火暴露行迹
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.67,1:00:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近身搏斗  抓住时机  坚定不移
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.34,1:00:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成功  便成仁
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.76,1:00:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗号是  "罗尚博"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.76,1:00:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}音似"向前冲"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.43,1:00:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明白吗  -罗尚博
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.60,1:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令已经下达  伙计们向前冲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.60,1:00:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此揭开  独立大业
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.02,1:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至交兄弟  征战八方
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.98,1:00:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南卡罗莱纳  劳伦斯写出英勇的新篇章
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.06,1:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有奴隶不再  自由才会到来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.86,1:00:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当英军鱼溃鸟散
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.78,1:00:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉法耶特早已经
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.15,1:00:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守在切萨皮克湾
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.70,1:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们何以确信  此计必将凯旋
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.53,1:00:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方内应  深入敌军  是的没错
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.91,1:00:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫丘利·穆里根
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.12,1:00:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁缝监视英国政府
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.75,1:00:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我量体裁衣  我搜集信息
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.29,1:00:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞒天过海
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.62,1:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为革命盟友通风报信
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.58,1:00:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,携手"自由之子"  有种就来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.58,1:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}反抗英国统治的激进秘密组织\N曾发动波士顿茶党事件  故俗称波士顿茶党
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.42,1:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招惹无赖  就是自讨苦吃
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.88,1:00:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身陷困境  谁来收烂摊子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.22,1:00:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫丘利·穆里根  早已声名远扬
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.34,1:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次被击倒  又一次次矗立
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.35,1:01:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向左  向右  稳住
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.52,1:01:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.11,1:01:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所畏惧  所向披靡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.67,1:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七日征战
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.96,1:01:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红衣军官  走上城墙
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.92,1:01:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥起白绢  我们放下枪炮
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.93,1:01:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争就这样终结
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.18,1:01:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们照顾伤员  我们缅怀死者
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.89,1:01:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑人士兵  白人士兵  一同思忖
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.89,1:01:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由是否触手可及
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.73,1:01:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为时尚早
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.81,1:01:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谈判投降条件
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.27,1:01:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见乔治·华盛顿笑容满面
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.73,1:01:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们押解英军出城
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.20,1:01:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人所剩无几  溃不成军
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.20,1:01:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民众走上街头  万人空巷
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.16,1:01:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们欢呼雀跃  教堂钟声齐天
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.54,1:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人落荒而逃
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.29,1:02:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们把酒言欢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.25,1:02:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.88,1:02:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.80,1:02:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.72,1:02:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.39,1:02:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天翻地覆  天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.40,1:02:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为美利坚自由而战  为法兰西自由而战
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.61,1:02:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天翻地覆  天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.94,1:02:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立新的国家  迎接我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.45,1:02:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天翻地覆  天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.78,1:02:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们胜利了  我们胜利了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.95,1:02:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们胜利了  我们胜利了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.41,1:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.36,1:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.67,1:03:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿替我承担  战争代价
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.70,1:03:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.22,1:03:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你勾结法国人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.97,1:03:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国和西班牙  同时对我开战
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.63,1:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好忧伤
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.70,1:03:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你走时  我们约法三章
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.51,1:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要唯我是瞻
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.03,1:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在  我们渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.53,1:03:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依旧要问你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.06,1:03:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一步何处去  你已获得自由
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.38,1:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你是否留意  掌权何其不易
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.07,1:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今你要自立
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.00,1:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真棒棒
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.28,1:04:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你是否明晰  今后何去何从
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.15,1:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沧海桑田  王朝兴替
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.46,1:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手握大权  进退两难
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.41,1:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大洋彼岸  孤掌难鸣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.20,1:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待到民怨沸腾日
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.22,1:04:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别向我来乞求
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.33,1:04:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今你要自立
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.61,1:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝西奥多莎  我该如何表达
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.14,1:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的双眸如我  名字随你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.57,1:05:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你呱呱坠地
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.37,1:05:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已满怀情愫
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.67,1:05:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻为你守护
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.36,1:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从不曾想过  眷恋家庭生活
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.96,1:05:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你笑容洋溢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.82,1:05:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已无力抗拒
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.48,1:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾自诩伶俐
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.23,1:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和这个国家  一同慢慢长大
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.25,1:05:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为你浴血奋战
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.40,1:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为你披襟斩棘
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.83,1:05:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我们能夯实根基
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.77,1:05:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将把它传承于你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.92,1:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给你整个天地  有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.92,1:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将震撼环宇
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.00,1:06:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将震撼环宇
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.46,1:06:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日  有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.39,1:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普啊  你的笑颜  让我沦陷
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.20,1:06:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.09,1:06:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着你啊  我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.02,1:06:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的骄傲  无言以表
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.34,1:06:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的内心  情绪万千
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.89,1:06:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普啊  你让朝阳黯然失色
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.80,1:06:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.96,1:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你笑容洋溢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.59,1:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已无力抗拒
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.71,1:06:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾自诩伶俐
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.59,1:06:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自幼父亲缺席
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.93,1:06:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自幼父亲缺席
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.41,1:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我一定要  伴你左右
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.25,1:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}伴你左右
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.68,1:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我会不惜一切
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.01,1:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}我会不断试错
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.23,1:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你撑起  世界祥和
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.58,1:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和这个国家  一同慢慢长大
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.22,1:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为你浴血奋战
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.37,1:07:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为你披襟斩棘
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.80,1:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我们能夯实根基
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.89,1:07:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将把它传承于你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.02,1:07:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给你整个天地
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.56,1:07:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将震撼环宇
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.15,1:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日  有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.64,1:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将震撼环宇
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.94,1:07:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日  有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.95,1:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有生之年  我见不到辉煌
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.10,1:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大  有你的信
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.09,1:08:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是约翰·劳伦斯  我等会再去读
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.23,1:08:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我欣然加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.92,1:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是他父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.14,1:08:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.34,1:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当后辈讲述我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.58,1:08:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以读给我听吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.70,1:08:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜的故事必将代代流传
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.10,1:08:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"周四  27日
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.81,1:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子在南卡罗莱纳
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.96,1:08:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与撤退途中的英军交火丧生
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.63,1:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争已经结束
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.32,1:08:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道  约翰梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.01,1:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放招募三千黑奴
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.12,1:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创建首支黑人军团
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.36,1:08:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着他逝去的  还有他的自由之梦"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.11,1:08:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们前赴后继
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.51,1:08:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.38,1:08:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命尚未成功
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.39,1:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争过后  我回到纽约
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.61,1:09:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争过后  我回到纽约
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.41,1:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完成学业  我从事法律工作
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.96,1:09:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从事法律工作  伯尔在隔壁工作
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.79,1:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管我们同时起家
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.38,1:09:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大迅速崭露头角
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.95,1:09:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又是如何  登上顶峰
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.92,1:09:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人啊  从不歇息
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.74,1:09:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位陪审成员  我实在太好奇  请允许我提问
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.73,1:09:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是否知道  我们正在创造历史
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.54,1:09:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是建国以来  首起谋杀案件
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.64,1:09:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审议基于自由
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.09,1:09:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}从不歇息
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.74,1:09:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拨开疑团
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.01,1:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,携助理律师  证明给你们看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.04,1:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合作律师  汉密尔顿  你坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.46,1:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的当事人李维·维克斯是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.33,1:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传唤首位证人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.41,1:09:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无须再多言
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.59,1:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  还有一事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.33,1:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么认定  就你聪明绝顶
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.86,1:09:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么认定  就你聪明绝顶
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.38,1:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么认定  就你聪明绝顶
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.02,1:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种态度  早晚万劫不复
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.64,1:09:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.23,1:09:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日夜笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.85,1:09:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天口诛笔伐  仿佛时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.44,1:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时  你斗争不止
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.68,1:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}从不歇息
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.40,1:10:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腐败堕落  我们早已司空见惯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.29,1:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最恶劣处  非奥巴尼莫属
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.54,1:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这块殖民地的经济愈发失控
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.91,1:10:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是政府需要我的原因
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.05,1:10:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}他从不歇息
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.69,1:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从事法律工作  我还完善法律
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.35,1:10:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次目睹世间不公  我都将其一一纠正
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.94,1:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候建立中央民主制
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.70,1:10:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不成功  我要效仿苏格拉底
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.93,1:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语言巨石  攻击平庸之辈
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.98,1:10:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  出席制宪会议
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.67,1:10:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被选中  参加制宪会议
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.27,1:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为纽约青年代表
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.75,1:10:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的话有些刺耳
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.47,1:10:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在会上提出自己对政体的提议
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.03,1:10:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.24,1:10:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对新政体他有自己的计划
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.34,1:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs12\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.63,1:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六小时唇枪舌战  议员们神思倦怠
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.32,1:10:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙有头脑
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.17,1:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人谁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.90,1:10:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你总直抒己见
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.52,1:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你总直抒己见
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.12,1:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每句宣言都令你成为众矢之的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.34,1:10:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛不合时宜
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.92,1:10:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日夜笔耕不辍  仿佛不合时宜
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.48,1:11:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天口诛笔伐  仿佛不合时宜
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.09,1:11:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少掺和
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.16,1:11:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.80,1:11:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚隆·伯尔  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.08,1:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已是午夜了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.32,1:11:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能谈谈吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.76,1:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是法务问题吗  -是的  这对我来说很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.35,1:11:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你有什么需要  -伯尔  你做律师比我在行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.25,1:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.75,1:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我说话又多又糙
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.65,1:11:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在法庭上十分出色  语言干练而有说服力
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.54,1:11:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的当事人需要有力的辩护  你能搞定
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.94,1:11:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的当事人是谁  -新美国《宪法》
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.13,1:11:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不行  -听我说完
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.31,1:11:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没门
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.03,1:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一系列匿名发表的文章
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.67,1:11:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向公众声援宪法
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.80,1:11:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没人会读的  -我认为有
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.35,1:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.19,1:11:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔  因此才需要它
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.37,1:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-《宪法》一塌糊涂  -因此才需要修订
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.10,1:11:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-充满矛盾  -独立也是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.48,1:11:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-万事开头难  -不  不行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.35,1:11:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你在犯错误  -晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.13,1:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等什么  你还犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.68,1:11:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们打赢了战争  图什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.51,1:11:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你支持新《宪法》吗  -当然
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.62,1:11:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就为它辩护  -万一你下错注呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.53,1:12:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔  我们一起学习  奋战  杀敌
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.01,1:12:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为如今我们所建国家的信念
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.66,1:12:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕此生仅有一次  你也应骄傲地表态
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.33,1:12:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白你怎能袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.32,1:12:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要将所有计划深藏不露
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.58,1:12:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待  等待  等待
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.58,1:12:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要作壁上观  见机行事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.66,1:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要静观其变
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.26,1:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着国家诞生
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.78,1:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着矛盾激化
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.18,1:12:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将向伦敦起航
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.99,1:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与一个慷慨多金的人同往
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.69,1:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到一位富有的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.69,1:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs12\b0\bord0\shad0}事实上安洁莉卡与汉密尔顿相遇时已嫁为人妇\N她与丈夫育有三女五子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.48,1:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将令我余生衣食无忧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.28,1:12:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不算有趣
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.85,1:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但论口才  谁也不可与你同日而语
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.88,1:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的亚历山大  -安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.37,1:12:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记写信
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.52,1:12:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你如今的成就
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.01,1:12:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想你曾一无所有
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.16,1:12:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着就是个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.80,1:13:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活着便已足够
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.11,1:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你能分给妻子一点时间
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.96,1:13:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我能为你带来安宁
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.44,1:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便足够吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.37,1:13:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大与詹姆斯·麦迪逊和约翰·杰伊联手
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.47,1:13:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写下一系列文章
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.82,1:13:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为新美国《宪法》辩护
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.19,1:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,题为《联邦论》
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.04,1:13:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划是共写25篇文章
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.49,1:13:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由三人平分工作量
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.61,1:13:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终  他们在六个月间写出85篇文章
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.01,1:13:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·杰伊写了五篇后病倒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.12,1:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯·麦迪逊写了29篇
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.85,1:13:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余51篇由汉密尔顿所写
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.94,1:13:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.49,1:13:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日夜笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.06,1:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天口诛笔伐  仿佛时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.68,1:13:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时日无多  是否时日无多
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.26,1:13:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛没有明天
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.06,1:13:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛命系笔尖
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.85,1:14:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  时刻争分夺秒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.37,1:14:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争分夺秒  争分夺秒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.34,1:14:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要我领导
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.99,1:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.44,1:14:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集所需之人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.28,1:14:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}请你担任副手
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.19,1:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}财政还是国务
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.41,1:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我明白这是不情之请
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.07,1:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}财政还是国务
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.03,1:14:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}离开你熟知的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.85,1:14:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  您想让我负责财政部还是国务院
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.24,1:14:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,财政部
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.84,1:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走起
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.88,1:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.21,1:14:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得离开
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.47,1:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.71,1:14:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看如今世事
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.52,1:14:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻我们活着是多么幸运
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.76,1:14:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}情难自禁
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.57,1:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要我领导
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.61,1:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}看这世事  这还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.22,1:14:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}他永远不会满足
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.47,1:14:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}如何才能满足
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.75,1:14:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}他永远不会满足
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.15,1:14:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}满足  满足
